            <Text fill="#769656" layoutX="29.0" layoutY="515.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="At each level of the game there will be several special squares in a random position, when you activate one of them its position changes. There is no marking that the slot is special. When activating a special slot the player must be notifiedAt each level of the game there should be 3 questions on the game board in random positions, immediately after answering a question a new question will appear in a random position" wrappingWidth="540.6062588504008" AnchorPane.leftAnchor="29.0" />
            <Text fill="#769656" layoutX="129.0" layoutY="713.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="First level for one minute: the horse moves like a regular horse in a chess game, the queen tries to reach a place that interferes with or harms the horse.Both the knight and the queen can leave the board and enter on the other side. There will be 3 random jump slots. " wrappingWidth="330.20995758086957" />
