            <Text fill="#769656" layoutX="129.0" layoutY="834.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="Second level for one minute: the horse moves two squares straight and one diagonally or two diagonally and one straight, the queen tries again to reach a place that disturbs the horse or harms it. Both the knight and the queen can leave the board and enter on the sideThe second. There will be 3 forget slots." wrappingWidth="330.20995758086957" />
